query:
INSERT INTO testimonials (clientName, clientTitle, rating, testimonialText, serviceUsed, featured, approved, createdAt, date)
VALUES
('Caroline', NULL, 5, 'I just have to say that All Resume Services has been a game changer for me. The new resume and cover letter they created for me have been getting me noticed by employers left and right. Before, I was applying everywhere with no success. Now, I''ve had 5 interviews already and been shortlisted twice! It''s amazing what a difference a good resume can make. Thank you so much Sonia and team—highly recommend!', NULL, 1, 1, NOW(), NULL),
('Jaisen Tanner', NULL, 5, 'I used your services back in 2015 having recently emigrated from Scotland. I landed two job interviews on the same day and was offered (and accepted) both casual positions. After a year as a casual, I am now full time permanent with Local Government and now have a senior position with a chance of acting up in the near future in a Co-ordinator role. I have recommended your services to friends looking to overhaul their resumes and thank you for the time and care you took 6 years ago which made a huge difference.', NULL, 1, 1, NOW(), '01/01/2015'),
('Stewart McGarth', NULL, 5, 'It was so good, it landed me my dream job in the Mining Industry!', NULL, 1, 1, NOW(), '01/10/2024'),
('Ashley QLD', NULL, 5, 'I paid for the resume and cover letter service and honestly was total surprised by the results. I want to thank Sonia for an amazing cover letter and a very professional resume. I thought I already had good resume but after seeing her version of my resume I realised why I wasn''t getting any interviews. It''s been 2-3 days since I got my resume and cover letter and I''ve already been called up by different recruiters. I definitely recommend getting this services as it is a essential investment into your future.', NULL, 1, 1, NOW(), 'March 2024'),
('QLD – March 2020', NULL, 5, 'Hello Sonia, Thank you very much for all of your help in answering my questions and giving me responses whenever required. I really appreciate your work done on my application. I will surely recommend your services. I have submitted my resume and cover letter today morning. I may give you more work in future. I am also looking for full time job as administration assistant / trainee accountant / graduate accountant. Whenever I will see a vacancy I will send you a link and would like you to prepare my cover letter and resume for me. Once again thank you so much for completing my cover letter and resume on time.Thank you, Kind regards', NULL, 1, 1, NOW(), NULL);
